data.description: NO HOA!! Espectacular back yard !!4 bedr and 4 full baths,  Better that New costruction with all upgrades ! Great open concept, Open sized fenced private back yard, outdoor entertainment area even includes a brand new drainage system The Kitchen is beautiful featuring granite countertops, a large island, stainless steel appliances and a separate breakfast area. A formal dining area provides plenty of space for holiday gatherings along with a cozy sitting room at the entry that could be used for a second living area, office or play room. Huge private and fenced back yard ,imagine your own pool in this fabulous land. The master suite features a double trey ceiling & a lot space to enjoy and relax. Enjoy 3,000 sq. feet of living. Quick access to 316 and Bethlehem shopping centers.Please ask for incentives . Apply until $12,000 in CC with our prefer lender AMERISBANK.
